2013;;A.C.O.D.;;American;;Stu Zicherman;;Adam Scott, Amy Poehler, Jessica Alba, Jane Lynch, Richard Jenkins;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A.C.O.D.;;A content and successful man decides to revisit a former counselor to make sense of his brother's wedding and his parents' extremely messy divorce. When he realizes his life has been personified in a book about children of divorce written by his mediocre counselor, he decides to confront his family about their dysfunctional nature.